Map Title : fy_shortrange
Map Version : Final
Author : SIL3NT.
E-mail : im_2_1337@hotmail.com

In this map you use the shotguns and grenades provided. This map is intended for a fast paced shotgun face off. The atmosphere has a grungy, scary feel that makes an intense fight. 

Thanks For your downloads and please COMMENT AND RATE!

Weapons: Pump Shotgun, Auto Shotgun, HE Grenade, Smoke Grenade
MAX Players: 64
INSTALL: Extract the map files to: C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\[YOURNAME]\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
